@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Hobbies";
}

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/hobbies.css" />
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="nav-title">
            <span class="my">My</span>
            <div class="nav-dropdown">
                <span class="nav-current">Hobbies</span>
                <div class="nav-dropdown-menu">
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Story">Story</a>
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Hobbies" class="active">Hobbies</a>
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Kitchen">Kitchen</a>
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Blog">Blog</a>
                    <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Projects">Projects</a>
                    <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/SachinOptics" target="_blank">My Shop ↗</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Blog" class="blog-btn"><span>Read My Blog</span></a>
    </header>

    <section class="page-hero">
        <div class="page-hero-content">
            <p class="page-label">What Makes Me Happy</p>
            <h1 class="page-title">My <span>Hobbies</span></h1>
            <p class="page-intro">Life isn't just about work. These are the passions that fill my days with joy, challenge, and a sense of play.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="hobbies-section">

        <!-- ========== HOBBY 1: PHOTOGRAPHY ========== -->
        <div class="hobby-feature">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1624913503273-5f9c4e980dba"
                 alt="Photo of Nikon Camera by Gift Habeshaw" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" title="Photo of Nikon Camera by Gift Habeshaw on Unsplash">
            <div class="hobby-content">
                <span class="hobby-number">01 — Primary Passion</span>
                <h2 class="hobby-title"><span>Photography</span></h2>
                <p class="hobby-desc">There's something magical about freezing a moment in time. Photography isn't just about taking pictures—it's about seeing the world differently, finding beauty in the ordinary, and telling stories without words.</p>
                <div class="hobby-stats">
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">4000+</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Photos Taken</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">Motorsport</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Favourite Style</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">Edinburgh</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Favourite City</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== HOBBY 2: SIM RACING & GAMING ========== -->
        <div class="hobby-feature">
            <img src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/55017655893_2bd794e463_b.jpg" alt="Photo of Aston Martin V8 Blackthorn at Silverstone" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;">
            <div class="hobby-content">
                <span class="hobby-number">02 — Digital Adrenaline</span>
                <h2 class="hobby-title">Sim Racing & <span>Gaming</span></h2>
                <p class="hobby-desc">There's something meditative about chasing the perfect lap. The precision required, the concentration, the muscle memory—it's art disguised as competition. Gaming taught me about narrative, composition, and emotional impact before I ever picked up a camera.</p>
                <div class="hobby-stats">
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">600+</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Hours on Track</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">AMR V8</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Favourite Car</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">Spa</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Best Circuit</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ========== HOBBY 3: COOKING & BAKING ========== -->
        <div class="hobby-feature">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1613119719948-d53865658a88" alt="Photo of Blueberry Muffins" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;" title="Photo of Blueberry Muffins by Aneta Voborilova on Unsplash">
            <div class="hobby-content">
                <span class="hobby-number">03 — Culinary Creativity</span>
                <h2 class="hobby-title">Cooking & <span>Baking</span></h2>
                <p class="hobby-desc">The kitchen is where creativity meets science. Whether it's perfecting a family recipe or experimenting with new flavour combinations, cooking is another form of artistic expression—one that feeds both the body and soul.</p>
                <div class="hobby-stats">
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">Cheesecake</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Favourite Dessert</div>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-number">Banana Bread</div>
                        <div class="hobby-stat-label">Best Bread</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

    <!-- PC & Desk Setup Section -->
    <section class="setup-section">
        <div class="setup-header">
            <h2>My <span>Setup</span></h2>
            <p>The tools I use to create, race, and work. My desk is where productivity meets passion.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="setup-grid">
            <!-- ========== UPDATE THESE SPECS WITH YOUR ACTUAL EQUIPMENT ========== -->
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">AMD Processor</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">Ryzen 7 7800X3D</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">8 Cores / 16 Threads</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">NVIDIA GPU</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">RTX 4070 Super</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">12GB of GDDR6X</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Memory</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">32GB DDR5</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">6000MHz</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Storage</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">6TB NVMe SSD</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">WD Black SN850X</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Main Monitor</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">34" WQHD 144Hz</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">VA Panel</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Keyboard</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">Mechanical</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">Cherry MX Browns</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Mouse</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">Logitech G502</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">Wired</div>
            </div>
            <div class="setup-card">
                <span class="setup-card-title">Racing Setup</span>
                <div class="setup-card-value">Logitech G29</div>
                <div class="setup-card-detail">Fanatec Pedals</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Other Interests Section -->
    <section class="interests-section">
        <div class="interests-header">
            <h2>Other <span>Interests</span></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="interests-grid">
            <div class="interest-card">
                <span class="interest-icon">🎵</span>
                <h3 class="interest-title">Music</h3>
                <p class="interest-desc">“One good thing about music, when it hits you, you feel no pain.” - Bob Marley</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
                <span class="interest-icon">☕</span>
                <h3 class="interest-title">Hot Chocolate</h3>
                <p class="interest-desc">Chocolate is the most wonderful thing in the world! Hot Chocolate is the most comforting way to enjoy it!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
                <span class="interest-icon">🏎️</span>
                <h3 class="interest-title">Formula 1</h3>
                <p class="interest-desc">"Patience is a virtue... but it's not something we F1 people have too much of" - Niki Lauda</p>
            </div>
            <div class="interest-card">
                <span class="interest-icon">🏁</span>
                <h3 class="interest-title">British GT</h3>
                <p class="interest-desc">
                    This is without doubt the most competitive domestic GT series in the world. To win here, you have to be bloody good and
                    you have to be consistent.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-brand">Sachin <span>Bhasin</span></div>
        <div class="footer-links">
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">Home</a>
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Story">Story</a>
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Hobbies" class="active">Hobbies</a>
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Kitchen">Kitchen</a>
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Blog">Blog</a>
            <a asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Projects">Projects</a>
            <a href="https://www.etsy.com/shop/SachinOptics" target="_blank">Shop</a>
        </div>
        <p class="footer-copyright">© @DateTime.UtcNow.Year Sachin Bhasin. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>